    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the<strong> remaining onion & grape chutney </strong>with 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [2 tbsp] </span><strong>olive oil</strong> in a large bowl</p><p>Add the<strong> salad</strong> and <strong>halved cherry tomatoes</strong> to the bowl and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>salad</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>three cheese melts with onion & grape chutney </strong>with the<strong> crispy potato slices</strong> and <strong>salad</strong> to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
